gujarati.context:
From the beginning to the end, this is seen; 
After that, love arises in you;
The state of famous children's home, after that it is considered as something valuable.

Who is my mother, who is my father; 
Who is my family, who is my relation;
My own soul is not satisfied with anyone's house.

Here is the translation:

Don't consider my body like that, then my whole soul will be in despair;
This wise saint understands, who has got a man of great wisdom.
